&lt;h2&gt;Aloha, my name is Whitney White&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	      Growing up, I practically lived on a horse in Olomana in addition to being raised with dogs, cats, rabbits, ducks… pretty much you name it!  Animals are my passion and my lifeline.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	 &lt;img class=&quot;f-left&quot; src=&quot;{{assets_img}}whitney.jpg&quot;&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	      Our Farm above is in Olinda…. Some may remember me as the owner of Starlight Farms “petting zoo”  or as current owner /operator of Interquest Detection Canines of Hawaii.  Some of you may know my husband, Mike.  We share the same values of honesty, responsibility, hard work and passion for what we do!  Both of our families have been in Hawaii for generations….we love and understand our Island home and community.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	      I, along with my PetPros team love, respect and passionately enjoy animals… often more than people!  But what sets us apart from others who also have that profile, is that we put safety and health of your pet as the top priority in our work as pet and home sitters.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	   As PetPros, we take our responsibilities very seriously! And we are excellent at it!
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;All of our PetPros:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	      We are professionals in the pet industry including vet technicians, dog trainers, livestock specialists and working dog handlers.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;dl&gt;
	&lt;dt&gt;Are Pet First Aid and CPR certified.&lt;/dt&gt;
	 &lt;dd&gt;In the event of an emergency, we have the training and resources to jump right into triage mode.&lt;/dd&gt;
	&lt;dt&gt;Have passed criminal background checks&lt;/dt&gt;
	 &lt;dd&gt;Can your neighbor or friend claim that?&lt;/dd&gt;
	&lt;dt&gt;Are fully bonded and insured&lt;/dt&gt;
	 &lt;dd&gt;Each PetPro is fully insured and bonded for your  pets and your security and peace of mind.&lt;/dd&gt;
	&lt;dt&gt;Have a love,compassion and understanding of all kinds of pets and animals well beyond the norm!&lt;/dt&gt;
&lt;/dl&gt;
&lt;h2&gt; Feel confident that your pet is in caring, honest and professional hands. &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Please call me at &lt;a href=&quot;tel:808-281-7075&quot;&gt;808-281-7075&lt;/a&gt; or visit our contact page so we can take care of you and your pet family!&lt;/h3&gt;
